Author: leoloewe19
Text: Please be patient with yourself. You can probably see that you're bloated, tell yourself it is impossible that it is all fat. But yeah, you will probably feel this way a bit longer. Tell yourself its not the reality and it will get better! Hang in there and give yourself some time!
